38const struct default_include cpp_include_defaults[]
39#ifdef INCLUDE_DEFAULTS
40= INCLUDE_DEFAULTS;
41#else
42= {
43#ifdef GPLUSPLUS_INCLUDE_DIR
44 /* Pick up GNU C++ generic include files. */
45 { GPLUSPLUS_INCLUDE_DIR, "G++", 1, 1,
46 GPLUSPLUS_INCLUDE_DIR_ADD_SYSROOT, 0 },
47#endif
48#ifdef GPLUSPLUS_TOOL_INCLUDE_DIR
49 /* Pick up GNU C++ target-dependent include files. */
50 { GPLUSPLUS_TOOL_INCLUDE_DIR, "G++", 1, 1,
51 GPLUSPLUS_INCLUDE_DIR_ADD_SYSROOT, 1 },
52#endif
53#ifdef GPLUSPLUS_BACKWARD_INCLUDE_DIR
54 /* Pick up GNU C++ backward and deprecated include files. */
55 { GPLUSPLUS_BACKWARD_INCLUDE_DIR, "G++", 1, 1,
56 GPLUSPLUS_INCLUDE_DIR_ADD_SYSROOT, 0 },
57#endif
58#ifdef GCC_INCLUDE_DIR
59#ifndef GCC_INCLUDE_DIR_ADD_SYSROOT
60#define GCC_INCLUDE_DIR_ADD_SYSROOT 0
61#endif
62 /* This is the dir for gcc's private headers. */
63 { GCC_INCLUDE_DIR, "GCC", 0, 0,
64 GCC_INCLUDE_DIR_ADD_SYSROOT, 0 },
65#endif
66#ifdef LOCAL_INCLUDE_DIR
67 /* /usr/local/include comes before the fixincluded header files. */
68 { LOCAL_INCLUDE_DIR, 0, 0, 1, 1, 2 },
69 { LOCAL_INCLUDE_DIR, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0 },
70#endif
71#ifdef PREFIX_INCLUDE_DIR
72 { PREFIX_INCLUDE_DIR, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0 },
73#endif
74#ifdef FIXED_INCLUDE_DIR
75 /* This is the dir for fixincludes. */
76 { FIXED_INCLUDE_DIR, "GCC", 0, 0, 0,
77 /* A multilib suffix needs adding if different multilibs use
78 different headers. */
79#ifdef SYSROOT_HEADERS_SUFFIX_SPEC
80 1
81#else
82 0
83#endif
84 },
85#endif
86#ifdef CROSS_INCLUDE_DIR
87 /* One place the target system's headers might be. */
88 { CROSS_INCLUDE_DIR, "GCC", 0, 0, 0, 0 },
89#endif
90#ifdef TOOL_INCLUDE_DIR
91 /* Another place the target system's headers might be. */
92 { TOOL_INCLUDE_DIR, "BINUTILS", 0, 1, 0, 0 },
93#endif
94#ifdef NATIVE_SYSTEM_HEADER_DIR
95 /* /usr/include comes dead last. */
96 { NATIVE_SYSTEM_HEADER_DIR, NATIVE_SYSTEM_HEADER_COMPONENT, 0, 0, 1, 2 },
97 { NATIVE_SYSTEM_HEADER_DIR, NATIVE_SYSTEM_HEADER_COMPONENT, 0, 0, 1, 0 },
98#endif
99 { 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0 }
100 };
101#endif /* no INCLUDE_DEFAULTS */

103#ifdef GCC_INCLUDE_DIR
104const char cpp_GCC_INCLUDE_DIR[] = GCC_INCLUDE_DIR;
105const size_t cpp_GCC_INCLUDE_DIR_len = sizeof GCC_INCLUDE_DIR - 8;
106#else
107const char cpp_GCC_INCLUDE_DIR[] = "";
108const size_t cpp_GCC_INCLUDE_DIR_len = 0;
109#endif
110
111/* The configured prefix. */
112const char cpp_PREFIX[] = PREFIX;
113const size_t cpp_PREFIX_len = sizeof PREFIX - 1;
114const char cpp_EXEC_PREFIX[] = STANDARD_EXEC_PREFIX;
115
116/* This value is set by cpp_relocated at runtime */
117const char *gcc_exec_prefix;
118
119/* Return true if the toolchain is relocated. */
120bool
121cpp_relocated (void)
122{
123 static int relocated = -1;
124
125 /* A relocated toolchain ignores standard include directories. */
126 if (relocated == -1)
127 {
128 /* Check if the toolchain was relocated? */
129 gcc_exec_prefix = getenv ("GCC_EXEC_PREFIX");
130 if (gcc_exec_prefix)
131 relocated = 1;
132 else
133 relocated = 0;
134 }
135
136 return relocated;
137}
